xronos: Client for the 'XRONOS' Chronological Database

Source: R/xronos-package.R
xronos-package.Rd

A programmatic interface to 'XRONOS' https://xronos.ch, a worldwide database of chronological information from archaeological contexts, including radiocarbon and dendrochronological data.
